<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">Korištenje alternativnih rasporeda tipkovnice</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents pagewide">
<p class="p">Tipkovnice dolaze s tisućama različitih rasporeda za različite jezike. Čak i za pojedinačni jezik, često postoji više rasporeda tipkovnice, poput Dvorak raspored za engleski. Možete postaviti vašu tipkovnicu da koristi drugi raspored, bez obzira na slova i simbole naslikane na tipkama. To je korisno ako često prebacujete između više jezika.</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Open the <span class="gui"><a href="shell-introduction.html.hr#activities" title="Aktivnosti pregled">Activities</a></span>
      overview and start typing <span class="gui">Keyboard</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Select <span class="guiseq"><span class="gui">Settings</span> ▸ <span class="gui">Keyboard</span></span> from the
      results. This will open the <span class="gui">Keyboard</span> panel.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Click the <span class="gui">+ Add Input Source…</span> button in the
      <span class="gui">Input Sources</span> section,
      select the language which is associated with the layout, then select a
      layout and press <span class="gui">Add</span>.</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
<div class="note note-tip" title="Savjet">
